snippet.title: Cloudberry Kingdom, We Like it Harder
snippet.description:
Cloudberry Kingdom, the land where good heroes go to die, and Bob is the best of them all. Bob sits on the precipice of retirement, recliner ready, but first he must get back what he lost years ago.

Jump and dodge your way through billions of levels on a last ditch mission to conquer infinity. The quest was never over. The princess was never saved. A challenge is waiting.

Art done by Tigar Hare Studios, find them at http://www.TigarHare.com !

Music is Blue Chair by Blind Digital, check them out at http://soundcloud.com/blind-digital !
